headline.main: Stella McCartney Brings Dance to Paris Opera for Fashion Week
headline.print_headline: Stella McCartney Brings Dance to Paris Opera for Fashion Week

lead_paragraph: Stella McCartney livened up the catwalk at Paris Fashion Week on Monday with dancing models wearing her signature over-sized clothes in trademark neutral shades with splashes of unusual colors.
